      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "When the pain feels this consuming, the idea of just stopping the fight can seem like the only relief. However, please know that these overwhelming feelings are often symptoms of deep distress, not a final truth about your life. Professional help doesn't just tell you to \"wait\"; therapy helps you build new ways to navigate the feeling of being stuck and reclaim your own sense of hope. If the urge is overwhelming, please call or text 988 immediately for immediate, compassionate support.",
